PrecisRegulations Amending the EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS by introducing PILOT PROJECT NO. 7, the purpose of which is to test whether or not calculating EI benefits based on the 14 weeks of employment where the claimant had the highest earnings would encourage them to accept all available work.
